[1] Case update
- Mon 19 Aug 2019. South Kivu (Mwenga) 3rd case
[Actualite, in French, machine trans., edited]
https://actualite.cd/2019/08/19/rdcebola-un-troisieme-cas-confirme-au-sud-kivu-et-une-nouvelle-zone-touchee-au-nord-kivu
A 3rd case of the Ebola epidemic has been confirmed in the territory of Mwenga, in the province of South Kivu, reports the technical secretariat in charge of the response. This 3rd case is diagnosed just 3 days after the official announcement of the disease in South Kivu where a death was recorded.

